The New Supply Chain Agenda  :  The Five Steps That Drive Real Value 
by Reuben E. Slone and Paul J. Dittmann and John T. Mentzer






Overview - Is your company delivering products to customers at the right time, place, and price--with the best possible availability and lowest possible cost and working capital? If not, you're probably alienating your customers and suppliers, eroding shareholder value, and losing control of your fixed costs.  Read more...

 


